This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. Implements a deliberately narrow subset of the JSON Schema
2020-12 specification (six keywords: type, required, properties, items,
enum, const). Schema and instance representation via swift-json (RFC
8259); failure paths via swift-jsonpointer (RFC 6901).

JSON Schema 2020-12: https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/release-notes
